    "summary": "During the call, we will be making certain forward-looking statements, including, but not limited to, statements regarding our 2025 guidance, our preliminary 2026 outlook, the medical cost trend and our projected MCRs, Medicaid rate adjustments and updates, our 2026 marketplace pricing and rate filings, our RFP awards, including our contract wins in Georgia and Texas as well as our M&A pipeline and activity, revenue growth related to RFP wins and M&A activity.  The recently enacted Big Beautiful Bill and expected Medicaid, Medicare and Marketplace program changes, our expected future growth in both our existing footprint and in the new products and markets and the estimated amount of our embedded earnings power.",
